<p>Providing your feedback is very simple. There is a <a href="http://forum.joomla.org/viewtopic.php?f=704&amp;t=781533" target="_blank">forum thread</a> where you can voice your concerns or express your support. All arguments will be carefully considered. The discussion will be open until 2 January 2013. Now is the time for your voice to be heard.</p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/598" target="_blank">Click here to read the proposal</a></p>
