<ul>
<li>Simplified foundational classes for Model, View and Controller</li>
<li>Database iterator</li>
<li>PostgreSQL driver</li>
<li>New Crypt package</li>
<li>File patcher</li>
</ul>
<p>The full list of commits is available here <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/commits/12.1">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/commits/12.1</a> and the api doc here <a href="http://api.joomla.org/">http://api.joomla.org</a></p>
